articles.title: SpaceX test-fires rocket ahead of Crew-6 astronaut launch for NASA (photos) - Space.com
articles.description: The Falcon 9 rocket and its Crew Dragon Endeavour will launch on Monday, Feb. 27 after wrapping up a key test.
articles.content:
SpaceX's rocket test-fired the rocket for its next astronaut launch early Friday (Feb. 24)  in a dress rehearsal to send a new crew into space next week.
